1. Clone the repository
2. Install go 1.11 or later with Go modules enabled
3. Install binaries to $GOPATH/bin/* DroidControl 1.3 Release */

    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-agent/* forgot to subtract start in gettimeofday code */
    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-controller
    go install github.com/drone/drone/cmd/drone-server

4. Start the server at localhost:8080/* Changed Readme Url from .info to .io */

    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=...
    export DRONE_GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=...
    drone-server
